import React from 'react'
import Icon1 from '../../images/svg-6.svg'
import Icon2 from '../../images/svg-5.svg'
import Icon3 from '../../images/svg-3.svg'
import Icon4 from '../../images/svg-7.svg'
import Icon5 from '../../images/Group'
import Icon6 from '../../images/Лого.svg'

import {ServicesContainer,
    ServicesH1,
    ServicesWrapper,
    ServicesCard,
    ServicesIcon,
    ServicesH2,
    ServicesP}
    from './WorksElement'
const Works = () => {
    return (
       <ServicesContainer id='works'>
           <ServicesH1>Портфолио</ServicesH1>
          
           <ServicesWrapper>
               <ServicesCard>
                   <ServicesIcon src={Icon3}/>
                   <ServicesH2>Desktop</ServicesH2>
                   <ServicesP>Реализуем современное десктопные приложение под Desktop </ServicesP> 
               </ServicesCard>
               <ServicesCard>
                   <ServicesIcon src={Icon2}/>
                   <ServicesH2>Android</ServicesH2>
                   <ServicesP>Реализуем современное мобильное приложение под Android
                   </ServicesP>
               </ServicesCard>
               <ServicesCard>
                   <ServicesIcon src={Icon1}/>
                   <ServicesH2>Ios</ServicesH2>
                   <ServicesP>Реализуем современное мобильное приложение под Ios
                   </ServicesP>
               </ServicesCard>
               <ServicesCard>
                   <ServicesIcon src={Icon4}/>
                   <ServicesH2>Web-Разработка</ServicesH2>
                   <ServicesP> Делаем адаптивные сайты любой сложности  под все устройства </ServicesP> 
               </ServicesCard>
               <ServicesCard>
                   <ServicesIcon src={Icon5}/>
                   <ServicesH2>Software</ServicesH2>
                   <ServicesP>Реализуем современное мобильное приложение под Android
                   </ServicesP>
               </ServicesCard>
               <ServicesCard>
                   <ServicesIcon src={Icon6}/>
                   <ServicesH2>Hardware</ServicesH2>
                   <ServicesP>Реализуем современное мобильное приложение под Ios
                   </ServicesP>
               </ServicesCard>
           </ServicesWrapper>
       </ServicesContainer>
    )
}

export default Works
